<section class="final-design prob">
 <%= image_tag("research.png") %>
  <p style="width: 70%; margin: 30px auto 0 auto; max-width: 1100px;"><span>Primary research finding from COVID-19 researchers:</span> the time allotted to digest one paper is 10+ minutes while key information needed is the article‚Äôs title, key findings, who/where, targets, context, models and methods (modelling, sequence, simulation, calculation). Time to digest this information and to conduct R&D would be reduced dramatically if this information was summarized at the beginning of the paper.</p>
